headline: After Painful Loss by Pats, Brady’s Future Is in Doubt
abstract: After throwing an interception on his final attempt in a playoff loss to the Tennessee Titans, Tom Brady offered little insight into whether his career with New England was over.
lead_paragraph: FOXBOROUGH, Mass. — With nine seconds left in what might have been his last game as a New England Patriot, Tom Brady was still trying to figure out what went wrong. A moment earlier, in his final act on the Gillette Stadium field late Saturday night, Brady threw a pass from his end zone that was deflected, then intercepted and returned for a touchdown.
